# Listing 1: search-form.html

<HTML>
<Head>
<Title>Search through the postings</Title>
</Head>

<Body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<H1>Search through the postings</H1>

<P>This form allows you to search through the posting to the ATF
forum.  Searches are <b>case-insensitive</b>, meaning that "ABC" is
the same as "abc".  This search only looks through the messages
associated with each thread.</P>

<Form method="POST" action="/cgi-bin/search.pl">

<P>Search for: <input type="text" name="term"></P>

<P>
<input type="radio" name="regexp" checked value="no">Literal search
<input type="radio" name="regexp" value="yes">Use regular expressions
</P>

<input type="submit" value="Search!">

</Form>
<P>
    <a href="/cgi-bin/post-comment-form.pl">[Post a message]</a>
    <a href="/cgi-bin/list-threads.pl">[View all threads]</a>
    <a href="/atf/search-form.html">[Search]</a>
    <a href="/atf/add-thread-form.html">[Add a new thread]</a>
    <a href="/atf/">[ATF home]</a>
</P>
